                "imgDesc": "<p>On Yashiori Island, there are two kinds of mechanical devices that suppress Tatarigami power. They are the Sacred Stone Mound and the Thunderbearer Mirror.</p>",
                "key": "Page 1/3"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/25750596/df07da247c09cc078e909d9812467ec5_2371689280979986881.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>When a Sacred Stone Mound is attacked, it can fire an electrical current in a specified direction. This current can remove the barriers formed by the Tatarigami's Will.</p>",
                "key": "Page 2/3"
              },
              {
                "img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/05/25750596/f808db9e143110041725cc1be753aeb2_3359758873686033267.png",
                "imgDesc": "<p>A Thunderbearer Mirror can receive the current fired by a Sacred Stone Mound and fire it back out in a different direction.</p>",
